summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5122 for the improvement of 9th Avenue West, from Olympic Way to a connection with existing pavement at intersection of Olympic Place and West Prospect Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 59004, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
